name: Diztinct
description:
We are a web design consultancy based near Faversham in Kent, UK. We provide a range of digital design services including responsive website design, brand identity and user interface design.
Diztinct was established in 2010 by Phil Mckeith who begun his career in 1999 as a graphic designer. His creative skills have been sought by many design agencies and high profile brands including Attik, Umbro, Asda Walmart and Nokia.
